premise_source_doc_sentence: Shift 2 : Unleashed  (  also known as Need for Speed : Shift 2 -- Unleashed  )  is a racing video game , and part of the Need for Speed series .
It is the second installment of the The Force Unleashed multimedia project , and the sequel to Star Wars : The Force Unleashed  (  2008  )  .

The main theme of Underworld Unleashed involved the new ruler of Hell , a demon-lord named Neron , offering many of the DC Universe supervillains and a number of the DC Universe superheroes various deals in which they would be given their greatest desires in exchange for their souls or for completing a task for him and the consequences of those deals .

As well as the core storyline of the three-issue Underworld Unleashed mini-series , most of the DC titles published in November and December 1995 and a number of one-shot issues were also part of the mini-series .
